{"word":"ὀψίζω","slug":"ὀψίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὀψίζω</b></el> <el>(ὀψίζω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ὀψέ'><el>ὀψέ</el></a>\n<p/><i>to do, go</i> or <i>come late</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ὀψισθέντες</el> <i>belated, benighted</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/>"}]}